  <Key>UNMATCHEDPURSUIT</Key>
  <Name>Unmatched Pursuit</Name>
  <Description>Once per game session, as an out of turn incidental, the character may spend 2 Destiny Points and designate one enemy character or vehicle within medium range (either personal or planetary scale) as his quarry. For the next 3 rounds if the designated target would successfully elude his pursuit, the character may voluntarily suffer 2 strain to keep pace, preventing the target from escaping him.</Description>
